What is a dream and what is reality...

481
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:25,460
It's hard to determine.

482
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:28,230
You must be weak.

483
00:37:28,230 --> 00:37:30,260
Is that it?

484
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:35,170
In spring of the 31st year of King
Seonjo, Year of Moosool, (1598)

485
00:37:35,170 --> 00:37:38,160
he was appointed to be the town
head of Hyupgok village in Gangwon province.

486
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:40,810
In the same year, on December 11th,

487
00:37:40,810 --> 00:37:43,680
at the young age of 27...

488
00:37:44,580 --> 00:37:45,740
he died.

489
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:53,090
Look here, how much more time is
left until the full moon in December?

490
00:37:54,720 --> 00:37:58,390
There are exactly 20 days left as of today.

491
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:05,160
Twenty days... Twenty days.

492
00:38:05,160 --> 00:38:12,170
My Lord. I am sorry to say this,
but after treating this woman

493
00:38:12,170 --> 00:38:17,410
I have found out that she is no ordinary being.

494
00:38:17,410 --> 00:38:22,050
If what the people said is right,
that she really is a mermaid,

495
00:38:22,050 --> 00:38:27,220
it seems like she won't be able
to recover if she stays here.

496
00:38:27,220 --> 00:38:30,390
Then, what should I do?

497
00:38:30,390 --> 00:38:34,330
You should hurry and send her back to the sea.

498
00:38:34,330 --> 00:38:39,160
I believe that is the way to save her life.

499
00:39:00,050 --> 00:39:03,060
Kim Dam Ryeong

500
00:39:04,020 --> 00:39:06,790
Why did he die so early?

501
00:39:06,790 --> 00:39:08,630
It's my age.

502
00:39:15,170 --> 00:39:18,270
Mom! I picked this up.  Mermaid Princess

