583
00:45:29,270 --> 00:45:35,810
When asked why he didn't erase the memories
when he was caught as his real self,

584
00:45:35,810 --> 00:45:40,990
he said that there were too many good
times to be able to erase those memories.

585
00:45:43,590 --> 00:45:46,490
He hoped that those memories
would stay with the person

586
00:45:46,490 --> 00:45:50,200
that he loved and would give
that person strength.

587
00:45:53,130 --> 00:45:55,800
I will be going now.

588
00:47:28,990 --> 00:47:31,760
What kind of bastard is that?

589
00:47:34,030 --> 00:47:39,470
What are you? You don't even have a
two-way radio. Are you really a cop?

590
00:47:53,890 --> 00:47:56,790
Department Head Ajussi Nam

591
00:48:11,270 --> 00:48:14,210
DepartmentHead Ajussi Nam

592
00:48:49,210 --> 00:48:51,580
That surprised me!

593
00:48:54,010 --> 00:48:56,050
Yeah, it's me.

594
00:48:57,280 --> 00:48:59,820
Oh, Heo Joon Jae.

595
00:48:59,820 --> 00:49:03,320
What's this? Why is your voice like that?
Are you sick?

596
00:49:04,390 --> 00:49:08,190
Yeah. I think I'm a bit sick.

597
00:49:08,190 --> 00:49:12,000
Where? Cheong, where are you? Are you at home?

598
00:49:13,330 --> 00:49:16,440
Why are you there?

599
00:49:16,440 --> 00:49:19,970
Stay there and wait. I will be right there.

600
00:49:28,280 --> 00:49:30,880
Is it you?

601
00:49:30,880 --> 00:49:36,190
The one who followed me not long ago and
pretended to be a cop in front of my house?

602
00:49:37,360 --> 00:49:40,960
Where is Ahjussi? Why do you have his cellphone?

603
00:49:40,960 --> 00:49:42,860
You have so many questions.

604
00:49:42,860 --> 00:49:44,150
Why do you suppose I have so many?

605
00:49:44,150 --> 00:49:47,100
It's because I want to get the
answers quickly and leave quickly.

606
00:49:47,100 --> 00:49:51,740
Someone is waiting for me
so I have to hurry and go.

607
00:49:51,740 --> 00:49:53,540
You can't go now.

608
00:51:24,830 --> 00:51:30,440
The address here is Yeon Heung Dong 29-21.
It's the building not yet sold.

609
00:51:30,440 --> 00:51:32,240
You can't come here with Tae
Oh within 30 minutes, right?

610
00:51:32,240 --> 00:51:35,470
No, it just feels weird.

611
00:51:35,470 --> 00:51:36,640
Should I call the police?

612
00:51:36,640 --> 00:51:38,880
Go ahead, so that I can get caught at the same time.

613
00:51:38,880 --> 00:51:41,750
Hey, if it's that strange then don't go in.

614
00:51:41,750 --> 00:51:47,220
Call some bullet taxis nearby.
They would be faster than the police.

615
00:51:47,220 --> 00:51:51,820
And don't forget to tell them to
honk the horn loudly when they come.

616
00:51:55,590 --> 00:51:59,730
Come out. You need to get your money.

617
00:52:04,640 --> 00:52:09,070
To the one who can go to Han River the
fastest, I will give ten times more.

618
00:52:09,070 --> 00:52:11,110
Here.

619
00:52:19,690 --> 00:52:23,320
Ahjussi, can you please go faster?

620
00:52:23,320 --> 00:52:25,090
Yes.

621
00:52:26,790 --> 00:52:30,630
The cellphone is turned off...

622
00:52:30,630 --> 00:52:33,600
In times like this,
she doesn't charge the battery.

623
00:52:34,570 --> 00:52:39,910
Please go faster. She's a bit sick and she's alone.

624
00:52:39,910 --> 00:52:42,370
Aren't you more hurt?

625
00:52:42,370 --> 00:52:44,610
Hurry and go.

